Pedrilliomorpha is a genus of beetles in the family Megalopodidae, containing the following species:
Pedrilliomorpha atrosuturalis Pic, 1917
Pedrilliomorpha bicolora Medvedev, 1996
Pedrilliomorpha clypealis Medvedev, 1996
Pedrilliomorpha gracilicornis Medvedev, 1996
Pedrilliomorpha nigrocincta Pic, 1924
Pedrilliomorpha riedeli Medvedev, 1996